agentOrchestrationConfig.description: Specifies whether profiling is enabled or disabled for the created profiling. See Agent Orchestration Config for more details.

computePlatform.description: Compute platform of the profiling group.

name.description:
Name of the profiling group.

The following arguments are optional:

tags.description: A map of tags assigned to the WorkSpaces Connection Alias. If configured with a provider `default_tags` configuration block present, tags with matching keys will overwrite those defined at the provider-level.

tagsAll.description: A map of tags assigned to the resource, including those inherited from the provider `default_tags` configuration block.
